      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients assigned probability distributions from literature meta-analysis. Monte Carlo UQ with 2000 samples performed; output NIH distributions reported at each operating point. A screening sensitivity study described in the UQ report narrative identifies wall shear stress exposure time and impeller tip clearance as potentially high-influence inputs; however, no structured sensitivity analysis record is linked to this package. Achieved level assessed as meeting required level based on the UQ coverage alone."
